icon-size-sm.description: Small icon size. Pairs with font-size 14px

h1.description: This is for component and layout headings. It pairs with $body-01.

h2.description: This is for smaller layout headings. It pairs with $body-02.

h3.description: This is for component and layout headings.

p.description: With a slightly taller line height than body-compact-01, this body style is used in productive layouts for long paragraphs with more than four lines. Use also for longer body copy in components such as accordion or structured list. It is always left-aligned. Body-long-01 can also be used for productive moments within expressive experiences.

label-01.description: This is a multipurpose type style that can be used for field labels in components, error messages, and captions. It should not be used for body copy.

label-02.description: This is a multipurpose type style that can be used for field labels in components, error messages, and captions. It should not be used for body copy.
